      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t应该是水电水利，这一块的油水随便一个小工程以十亿起步，各项监督又属于灯下黑.光是项目采购一项就可以碾压医疗教育房地产的总和.<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNmZhNmM3MzIyZTcyMTk4OGEzN2QxLmpwZz93aWR0aD02ODAmaGVpZ2h0PTUwMQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6fa6c7322e721988a37d1.jpg?width=680&amp;height=501\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6fa6c7322e721988a37d1.jpg?width=680&amp;height=501\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6fa6c7322e721988a37d1.jpg?width=680&amp;height=501\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
